headline: New business bookings drive ADP Q3 25 revenue growth
summary: Automatic Data Processing, Inc. released its Q3 25 financial results on April 30, 2025. The company saw a 5.7% y/y increase in revenues, reaching $5.6bn. This growth was driven by new business...
